{"id":10073,"date":"2012-11-28T00:37:38","date_gmt":"2012-11-28T05:37:38","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=10073"},"modified":"2019-09-20T11:07:59","modified_gmt":"2019-09-20T07:07:59","slug":"haram-animals-targets","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/28\/haram-animals-targets\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Animals: Forbidden to use living animals as targets"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Sa\u2019id ibn Jubayr reported: I was with Ibn Umar, may Allah be pleased with him, when we passed by a group who had tied down a chicken and they were using it as a target. When they saw Ibn Umar, they fled and left it behind. Ibn Umar said, \u201cWho has done this? The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, has cursed whoever has done this.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>In another narration, Ibn Umar said, &#8220;The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, has cursed whoever takes something with a soul as his target.&#8221;<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5196,\u00a0S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1958<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <em><strong>Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0<\/strong><\/em>(authenticity agreed upon) according\u00a0to Al-Bukhari and Muslim<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u062c\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064f\u0646\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0639\u0650\u0646\u0652\u062f\u064e \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647 \u0641\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064f\u0651\u0648\u0627 \u0628\u0650\u0641\u0650\u062a\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0629\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0648\u0652 \u0628\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0641\u064e\u0631\u064d \u0646\u064e\u0635\u064e\u0628\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u062f\u064e\u062c\u064e\u0627\u062c\u064e\u0629\u064b \u064a\u064e\u0631\u0652\u06